an exception can be handled using try catch and finally block
it is possible to handle multiiple excepiton using multiple catch block
a single try block can be followed by a several catch block
we can't write a catch without try block vbut a try block can be written without any catch 
we can't insert statement bw try and catch
it is possible to write a ctry block with oiin another try block called nested try block
sometime user don't want to handle the exception then programmer can use throw /throws  